  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a randomized study of standard versus extra ostomy education.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate the effectiveness of pre-operative and
      post-operative ostomy education compared to standard of care ostomy education.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
